{"tid":2001448,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"『突破樽頸位』之 分化戰線要人！","createTime":"2020-05-04T13:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T16:32:39.000Z","uid":165234,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"055cd4d14a0bb68191690a1a5c880386c7562ee6","tid":2001448,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T13:59:41.000Z","msg":"作為鍵盤戰士已有十多年經驗！<br />\n<br />\n以下將為你提供三個簡單步驟分化藍絲！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3QqCRWb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3QqCRWb.jpg&h=9f4c543a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><em>第一步 &mdash; 角色定位</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n你係新移民？本土愛國藍絲？支那居港人士？<br />\n<br />\n你係咩立場？撐政府？撐警？定係仇港？<br />\n<br />\n咩職業？香港基層？支那投資者？失業人士？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">角色定位係極為關鍵嘅一環 用同理心令到藍絲感觸 從而煽動仇恨</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y4VZ5kq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY4VZ5kq.jpg&h=6262bafb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><em>第二步 &mdash; 前置工作</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n完善化你既角色 用戶名同頭像可以更進取 <br />\n<br />\ne.g. 用戶名：反對暴徒亂港 永遠支持警隊<br />\n頭像： 鄧炳強<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(切勿模稜兩可 e.g. 用戶名：撐警反政府)<br />\n(藍絲會因為你既用户名模稜兩可而對你既留言有先入為主既不信任)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記住要呃到敵人 首先要呃到自己人</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TYROeiB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTYROeiB.jpg&h=dc40d926&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><em>第三步 &mdash; Take Action</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n用上述角色以及文章做例子<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎｜連續15日本地零感染　張竹君感安樂：要守得住輸入個案<br />\n<br />\n(age: 48 本土廢老 中學學歷水平)<br />\n用戶名：反對暴徒亂港 永遠支持警隊<br />\n頭像： 鄧炳強<br />\n留言：吊你林鄭 知唔知幾多警察中新冠肺炎 你做過咩？有冇探訪佢哋照顧佢地屋企人？<br />\n<br />\n(age: 55 新移民廢老 小學學歷水平)<br />\n用戶名： 死曱甴 卜街<br />\n頭像： 蟑螂<br />\n留言：我就黎没饭开 地盘五要人牙衣加 警察加甘多人工 阿叔就黎食树皮拉 牙仔一日食得一餐炸<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(5P字轉支體文字 嘩 個feel出哂嚟)</span><br />\n<br />\n(age: 39 新移民 小學學歷水平)<br />\n用戶名： 香港要和平 <br />\n頭像： BB用品<br />\n留言：我小孩 两三个月没上幼儿园了 很惨 香港政府 到底想什么样 你妈B 林郑<br />\n<br />\n本人最喜歡既分化戰場係香港01同YouTube<br />\n <br />\n香港01藍之餘同時模稜兩可 部份文章好易落手<br />\n<br />\n而YouTube人流多 同時好多藍KOL 同樣易落手<br />\n<br />\n總結：<br />\n融入你自己嘅角色 堅定你做出嚟角色嘅立場 <br />\n盡量喺藍絲場留言 以免製造藍絲過多嘅假像 <br />\n分散投資 唔好喺同一個post 糾纏太耐<br />\n可以嘅話盡量第一個留言 好容易造成風向<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"8051a50e3f0a33936c793dce2af4d57ce57bf5d9","tid":2001448,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:01:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ae2166b84ed3d83102862b8b0b762e24853dabe4","tid":2001448,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:03:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f584c1f6a4d6626e8cf02c332fc3f838cc887e7a","tid":2001448,"uid":162046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:20:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ccff71eb97f72a63c1f156d16c0d068e7307b84","tid":2001448,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:32:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bf26ef39cc1de660f7546961821dc25c2a935748","tid":2001448,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:37:48.000Z","msg":"有任務"},{"pid":"148483c11241dc236716b32965492ddee74f0b2a","tid":2001448,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:38:22.000Z","msg":"出嚟啦連登間諜"},{"pid":"e00ebac2b01aac689bf0df6bfa357d981dce9d27","tid":2001448,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:39:32.000Z","msg":"特務連連狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25cf59102266c8226010cc1d6479ffde1ccb16e1","tid":2001448,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75355278d1cd325164bef091ebb6f5084d2e189","tid":2001448,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:32:39.000Z","msg